                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-sergeant</hi>, 316). I received a half crown from Mr. Day, and gave it to Kinahan.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18520405-name-651" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18520405-name-651" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
