                        <interp inst="t18520405-name-651" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM WEBSTER</persName>
                  </hi>. I am inspector of coin to the Royal Mint. These last two half crowns are bad, and this one passed before is also bad.</p>
